      "content": "In the agent card header in `public/app.js`, swap the order of slot and name so name comes first, slot second.\n\nFind the agent card identity HTML in `renderAgents()`:\n```javascript\n<div class=\"agent-card-identity\">\n  <span class=\"agent-slot\">${esc(slot)}</span>\n  <span class=\"agent-name\">${humanName || 'agent'}</span>\n</div>\n```\n\nChange it to:\n```javascript\n<div class=\"agent-card-identity\">\n  <span class=\"agent-name\">${humanName || 'agent'}</span>\n  <span class=\"agent-slot\">${esc(slot)}</span>\n</div>\n```\n\nThat's the only change. Commit: `style: agent card — name before slot in header`\n\nReport DONE to cec50b17:0.",
